USEPA is proposing to temporarily lift (i.e., toll)

4

 the highway and offset sanctions imposed under section 110(m) upon the passage by the Indiana legislature and signature
by the Governor of legislation which USEPA preliminary determines provides legal authority for an enhanced I/M program
